==German==
===Suffix===
# Converts an adjective into a noun and usually denotes an abstract quality of the adjectival root. -keit is used after the adjective endings [[-ig]], [[-ich]], [[-sam]], and [[-bar]]. It is often equivalent to the English suffix [[-ness]]
#:The woman is '''beautiful'''. &rarr; ''Die Frau ist '''schön'''.'' 
#:'''Beauty''' is in the eye of the beholder. &rarr; '''''Schönheit''' liegt im Auge des Betrachters.''
